    <scopecontent id="aspace_36872b6a1ec72d1f72b0b8362f7f3015">
      <head>Scope and Contents</head>
      <p>This collection largely consists of Mayer's writings, in both final and draft form. There
        is a small amount of printed correspondence, including with notable economists Milton
        Friedman, Roger Backhouse, and others. The bulk of the collection consists of born-digital
        material, which contain both drafts and email correspondence.</p>
    </scopecontent>
